This is a brand page for the SUN COFFEE ROASTERS trademark by Sun Coffee Roasters, LLC 
                                in Plainville, CT, 06062.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this SUN COFFEE ROASTERS trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Sun Coffee Roasters, LLC of the SUN COFFEE ROASTERS trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the SUN COFFEE ROASTERS trademark.
                           






On Tuesday, December 29, 2009,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        SUN COFFEE ROASTERS by 
                        Sun Coffee Roasters, LLC, Plainville, CT  06062.
                        The USPTO has given the SUN COFFEE ROASTERS 
                        trademark serial  number of  77901974.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is CONTINUED USE AND INCONTESTIBILITY ACCEPTED.
                        The correspondent listed for SUN COFFEE ROASTERS is 
                        
                        
                                            Wm. Tucker Griffith of 
                                            McCormick, Paulding & Huber LLP,  185 Asylum Street, HARTFORD CT 06103 
                                .
                            The SUN COFFEE ROASTERS trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Treatment & Processing of Materials Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for SUN COFFEE ROASTERS 
                            is Coffee roasting and processing. 
                            





