 Mark Description: 
The mark consists of a green border, surrounding a cream border, framing a red background within which lies a top down or bird's eye view of a white coffee cup. Inside the coffee cup is a brown image of a sun against a brown background, with brown steam rising from the upper left portion of the coffee cup, all above the stylized wording "Sun Coffee Roasters" with the word "Sun" in white and the words "Coffee Roasters" in brown.


