Artisan BBQ Coffee Roaster
We have four different capacity artisan all-in-one combo outdoor bbq coffee roaster grill systems.   Each system is available with or without a grill.  Note that if you purchase a system with a grill we can only deliver the grill portion of the order to U.S. Mainland States.  If you decide to purchase a BBQ Coffee Roaster without a grill please note that your own grill must be the same (for the 20 or 10 lb. systems) or similar to the grill (for the 5 or 1 lb. systems) intended for use with the applicable system.  All systems (except the 1 lb. version) include our High Speed 60RPM Motor system.  The 1 lb. version (miniROAST-BBQ) includes the Char Broil Premium Rotisserie 6RPM motor assembly which is more than adequate for the lower bean capacity roast.   If you have any questions on whether your grill can be used with a particular system please contact us before purchase as grill measurements are critical for system fit.  Setup and usage manual included with purchase.
These artisan combo systems are great for Farmers Markets and start up roasting businesses.  Save tens of thousands of dollars vs. the cost of a conventional commercial roaster with one today!

To order go to top of this listing and "Choose an option" then "Add to cart" and then either continue shopping or checkout from there.

Following is a description of each available system:
Best Value: megaROAST-BBQ
The megaROAST-BBQ is a 20 lb. capacity BBQ Coffee Roaster system comprised of our 20 lb. capacity All Stainless Steel drum, integrated with our own specially designed rod assembly and our QuikSPIN-CRC high speed motor system.  This system is designed only to fit the Char Broil K6B 6-Burner Grill.  It will not fit any other grill and we do not make it to fit any other grill.  Grill can be purchased from us as an add-on or you may purchase it directly from Amazon at this link.  (Grill must be from Amazon as there are different configurations of the Char Broil K6B 6-burner grill and our system will only fit the Amazon version.)  Propane tank for grill not included with purchase.
supremeROAST-BBQ
The supremeROAST-BBQ is a 10 lb. capacity BBQ Coffee Roaster system comprised of our 10 lb. capacity All Stainless Steel drum, integrated with our own specially designed rod assembly and our QuikSPIN-CRC high speed motor system.  This system is designed only to fit the Char Broil K6B 6-Burner Grill.  It will not fit any other grill and we do not make it to fit any other grill.  Grill can be purchased from us as an add-on or you may purchase it directly from Amazon at this link.  (Grill must be from Amazon as there are different configurations of the Char Broil K6B 6-burner grill and our system will only fit the Amazon version.)  Propane tank for grill not included with purchase.
premiumROAST-BBQ
The premiumROAST-BBQ is a 5 lb. capacity BBQ Coffee Roaster system comprised of our 5 lb. capacity All Stainless Steel drum, integrated with our own specially designed rod assembly and our QuikSPIN-CRC high speed motor system.  This system is designed to fit the Char Broil Classic 4-Burner Grill.  Grill can be purchased from us as an add-on or you may purchase it directly from Amazon at this link.   This system may fit other grills so if you have a particular grill in mind and wish to see if our system will fit please contact us prior to purchase.  Propane tank for grill not included with purchase.
Great For Beginners:  miniROAST-BBQ
(see video)
The miniROAST-BBQ is a 1 lb. capacity BBQ Coffee Roaster system comprised of our 1 lb. capacity All Stainless Steel drum, integrated with the Char Broil Premium Universal Fit rotisserie.  This system is designed to fit the Char Broil Classic 300 2-Burner Grill.  Grill can be purchased from us as an add-on for use with this system or you may purchase it directly from Amazon at this link.  This system may fit other grills so if you have a particular grill in mind and wish to see if our system will fit please contact us prior to purchase.  Propane tank for grill not included with purchase.

